title: Диагноз «Везучая»
overview: Sociopath Lika is endowed with an incredible gift to bring good luck in any scam, moonlighting as a kind of "talisman" in criminal circles. But when one of the criminal authorities decides to make Lika his personal talisman, she is forced to embark on an adventure along with Anton, an unfair accountant, who is unjustly accused of money laundering through a charitable foundation. The heroine will try to prove Anton's innocence, as well as restore his relationship with his daughter Stesha.
